    "Automated analysis of function use, where and how they are accessed and typical calling behavior by autonomous agents enables IAM policies to be improved as needed, without involving the developers and the chance of overly permissive roles appearing.",
    "DevOps Cultural ShiftMohammed (2011) highlights the way DevOps changes organizational culture, encouraging stability, agility and workers in development and operations to cooperate more closely.",
    "The paper points out the need to use automation to streamline operations.",
    "Also, managing IAM policies must be faster and smarter, so they can be automated.Because these security agents are equipped with machine learning and can understand policies, they can give optimal IAM hardening in the current DevOps cycle.",
